f.d:
zhing gi rgyud rgyan shin tu brtan par grub/ / dri med dri bral 'od 'gyed snying po can/ / nor bu pad+mo rgya mtsho kun la gnas/ / la la gang+gA'i rgya mtsho dag la gnas; ;
rnam pa sna tshogs tshul gyi gzhi gnas shing / / dbyibs kyang sna tshogs kha dog gzugs kyang mang / / ri rab grong khyer shing gi dkyil 'khor dang / / zhing rgyud thams cad la la phyogs kun lta; ;
la la 'od lus me tog snying po can/ / nor bus byas pa kun nas sprin dang chu/ / la la'i rgyud gsal mu tig 'od zer lus/ / nor bu'i gzhi gnas kun kyang mi shigs sra/ /
'byams klas la la kha dog sna tshogs gsal/ / 'od 'dra 'od 'phro me mar sprin gyi mdog / la la'i rgyud ni sgra dang skad kyi lus/ / de las sangs rgyas gsung dbyangs mtha' yas 'byung / /
la la'i rgyud ni smon lam sgra yi lus/ / spyod pa rnam 'phrul sprin gyi sgra yi lus/ / la la bsod nams yangs dang las kyi sgra/ / la la'i lus ni rgyal ba'i yon tan sgra; ;
zhing gi rgyud rnams rgya mtsho bsam yas pa/ / kun nas mi zad du ma'i sgo nas 'jug / rnam 'phrul yangs pa mi zad rgyan gyi rnams/ / tshad med kun gyis phyogs kun rgyas par 'gengs/ /
phyogs rnams kun tu zhing rnams 'du 'gyur te/ / yangs pa'i tshul gyis zhing gi rgyud zhugs par/ / phyogs bcu kun tu 'du bar snang ba yang / / 'gro ba med cing 'jug pa yod pa min/ /
tshul gcig gis ni rgyud rnams kun kyang 'gengs/ / thams cad ma lus re rer rab tu 'dug / de la tha dad gang yang mi dmigs te/ / gzhi med kun 'gengs mtha' dang dbus kyang med/ /
zhing rnams tshul gyi rgyud la rnam 'phrul ba/ / sangs rgyas rnam snang mdzad pa kun nas snang / / smon lam sgra ni rgya mtshor rab brjod cing / / zhing gi dbyings na sems can kun kyang 'dul/ /
zhing rnams sangs rgyas sku yis kun khyab snang / / bsam gyis mi khyab byang chub sems dpas gang / / sangs rgyas rnam 'phrul mi mnyam stobs ston cing / / sems can mang po tshad med rnam par 'dul/ /

de dag la sogs pa spos chu'i rgya mtsho sangs rgyas kyi zhing brjod du med pa'i yang brjod du med pa'i rdul shin tu phra ba snyed kyi phyi rol lho phyogs logs kyi 'khor yug gi mtshams na spos chu'i rgya mtsho gzhi 'khor lo tshad med pas brgyan pa zhes bya ba yod de/ de la 'jig rten gyi khams kyi rgyud phyogs tshad med pa snrel zhi zhes bya ba zhing gi rgyud yon tan sna tshogs thams cad shin tu ston pa'i sgra'i lhun can rab tu gnas te/ de thams cad kyi 'og na 'jig rten gyi khams rdo rje me tog gis khyab pa zhes bya ba yod de/ de na de bzhin gshegs pa mtshan mi zad pa'i 'od zer sgo kun nas sgrog pa zhes bya ba bzhugs so; ;
de'i steng na 'jig rten gyi khams sangs rgyas kyi zhing bcu'i rdul shin tu phra ba snyed 'das pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams kyi rgyud na 'jig rten gyi khams rdo rje'i rgyal mtshan gzhi mnyam pa yod pa de na 'jig rten gyi khams rin po che'i gos kyi rgyal mtshan 'byung ba zhes bya ba yod de/ de na de bzhin gshegs pa bsod nams kyi sprin kun tu dpal gyi gzi brjid ces bya ba bzhugs so; ;
de'i steng na 'jig rten gyi khams gzhi mnyam pa mi mjed ces bya ba yod pa de na 'jig rten gyi khams rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa zhes bya ba yod de/ de na de bzhin gshegs pa khyad par gyi blo gros rgya mtsho zhes bya ba bzhugs so/ /
de'i steng na 'jig rten gyi khams kyi rgyud kyi dang po la 'jig rten gyi khams nyi ma'i mig gi rgyal mtshan zhes bya ba yod de/ de na de bzhin gshegs pa ye shes kyi nyi ma pad+mo'i sprin ces bya ba bzhugs so/ /
